snippet.textDisplay:
Daisuke Amaya created the program used to synthesize this song, Orgview, and sequenced this and all other Cave Story in his free time.  He worked as a salaryman in Japan while creating this.

I often wonder at the hidden brilliance in the masses, waiting to be tapped, what other Moonsongs are out there.

I think the time I invested in Cavestory was well worth it, and this theme makes me realize that

snippet.textDisplay:
I like a game with a little bite to it. It's way better than those games that pat you on the head and whisper sweet nothings to you when you fail, assuring you that you haven't really failed at all.
Oh, your screen turned red? Just hide. It's a minor inconvenience. Get back up. You're doing great!
DON'T. PATRONIZE. ME.
